yi said two hospitals did not admit the victim. Further information revealed that the deceased was coming from the office around 8 pm on Tuesday evening when some gunmen trying to snatch the bike from the owner. While the attackers were resisted, they shot the deceased at close range. In a similar situation, a young man identified as Adoja Tanaku was reportedly beheaded during an argument at Bakatare area of Ibadan very close to Ogun State. Vanguard News Nigeria By Adeola Badru GOVERNOR Seyi Makinde of Oyo State has reiterated his commitment that no region in the state would be deprived or denied enjoying the wave of socio-economic development currently spreading across the state. The governor spoke yesterday, through the Commissioner for Local Government and Chieftaincy Matters, Mrs Funmilayo… July 30, 2020 In "News" By Adeola Badru Governor Seyi Makinde of Oyo State has reiterated his commitment that no region in the state would be deprived or denied enjoying the wave of socio-economic development currently spreading across the state. The governor spoke yesterday, through the Commissioner for Local Government and Chieftaincy Matters, Mrs Funmilayo… July 30, 2020 In "News" Gov. Seyi Makinde of Oyo State on Tuesday pledged to support Traditional institutions and promised not to interfere in the Ibadan traditional chieftaincy system, but work to achieve its desired goals. The governor gave the assurance during the 86th birthday anniversary and chieftaincy celebration of High Chief (Mrs) Theresa Oyekanmi.… October 1, 2019 In "News"